{
  "id": "63bfff836668d9001d4a57ce",
  "title": "機能和声",
  "created": 1673527175,
  "updated": 1675964926,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63bfff836668d9001d4a57ce",
      "text": "機能和声",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673527175,
      "updated": 1673527175
    },
    {
      "id": "63bfff86aff09e0000e5304a",
      "text": ">[機能和声理論]は、[ジャン＝フィリップ・ラモー]が[和声]のために諸[三和音]の各機能を、機能という言葉を使うことなく『和声論』（1722年）で個別化区分した後に、[フーゴー・リーマン]が1893年に体系化し、[ヴィルヘルム・マーラー]がBeitrag zur durmolltonalen Harmonielehreを1931年に出版して拡大させた理論である。日本ではHarmonielehreのlehreにあやかって「[機能和声学]」と呼ばれることがある。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673527175,
      "updated": 1673527660
    },
    {
      "id": "63bfffbfaff09e0000e5304e",
      "text": "\thttps://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/機能和声理論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673527232,
      "updated": 1673838152
    },
    {
      "id": "63bfffccaff09e0000e53050",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673527245,
      "updated": 1673527245
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4be48aff09e0000f2f097",
      "text": "[コードの機能]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673838153,
      "updated": 1673838154
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4be4aaff09e0000f2f098",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673838154,
      "updated": 1673838154
    },
    {
      "id": "63bfffebaff09e0000e53051",
      "text": ">[キルンベルガー]は、数字付き低音のみで和声を示す従来の方法から一歩抜きんでて、長旋法あるいは短旋法の音度に基づくローマ数字による和声分析を用いた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673527275,
      "updated": 1673527531
    },
    {
      "id": "63bfffecaff09e0000e53052",
      "text": "\t→https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/ローマ数字による和声分析",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673527276,
      "updated": 1673527307
    },
    {
      "id": "63bfffeeaff09e0000e53055",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/3008376f16b9657dd3583320e9f82793]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673527278,
      "updated": 1673527319
    },
    {
      "id": "63c00024aff09e0000e53057",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673527333,
      "updated": 1673527333
    },
    {
      "id": "63c00017aff09e0000e53056",
      "text": ">ローマ数字による和声分析では不十分と感じた[フーゴー・リーマン]はローマ数字による音度ではなく、[トニカ]をT, [ドミナント]をD, [サブドミナント]をSとする記号を用いた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673527319,
      "updated": 1673527687
    },
    {
      "id": "63c01b44aff09e0000216306",
      "text": " [tonic] [トニック]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673534276,
      "updated": 1673838176
    },
    {
      "id": "63c01b5aaff09e0000216309",
      "text": " [dominant] [ドミナント]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673534299,
      "updated": 1673838176
    },
    {
      "id": "63c01b5aaff09e000021630a",
      "text": " [subdominant] [サブドミナント]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673534299,
      "updated": 1673838176
    },
    {
      "id": "63c01b5aaff09e000021630b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673534299,
      "updated": 1673534299
    },
    {
      "id": "63c01b5aaff09e000021630c",
      "text": " [ダイアトニックコード]を機能ごとに分類したやつ[who.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673534299,
      "updated": 1673534299
    },
    {
      "id": "63c01b5aaff09e000021630d",
      "text": " 　ダイアトニックコードに限らないかも",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673534299,
      "updated": 1673534299
    },
    {
      "id": "63c01b5aaff09e000021630e",
      "text": "\t「分類」ではない理解[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673534299,
      "updated": 1673539903
    },
    {
      "id": "63c030f8aff09e00000f34c0",
      "text": "\t\tVがdominant, IVがsubdominant",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673539832,
      "updated": 1673539841
    },
    {
      "id": "63c03101aff09e00000f34c1",
      "text": " \t\t[https://gyazo.com/6fb6b042132865e7a3aedf088deed4ea]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673539841,
      "updated": 1673539841
    },
    {
      "id": "63c03101aff09e00000f34c2",
      "text": " \t\t\t[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Function_(music) Function (music) - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673539841,
      "updated": 1673539841
    },
    {
      "id": "63c03101aff09e00000f34c3",
      "text": " \t\t\t\tこれの日本語版が [https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/機能和声理論 機能和声理論 - Wikipedia]  #機能和声",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673539841,
      "updated": 1673539841
    },
    {
      "id": "63c03101aff09e00000f34c4",
      "text": "\t\t[完全五度]上がるのがdominant、下がるのがsubdominant",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673539841,
      "updated": 1673539850
    },
    {
      "id": "63c03109aff09e00000f34c5",
      "text": " \t\t[https://gyazo.com/a671db1266ba65cecfd901f0afd23aa0][src https://www.schoolofcomposition.com/technical-names-in-music/11-tonic-dominant-and-subdominant-c-g-f/]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673539850,
      "updated": 1673539850
    },
    {
      "id": "63c03109aff09e00000f34c6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673539850,
      "updated": 1673539850
    },
    {
      "id": "63c01b5aaff09e000021630f",
      "text": "\t\t狭義と広義があるのかな？[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673534299,
      "updated": 1673539864
    },
    {
      "id": "63c01b5aaff09e0000216310",
      "text": "\t\t キーがCのときこういう説明を見ます[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673534299,
      "updated": 1673534299
    },
    {
      "id": "63c01b5aaff09e0000216311",
      "text": "\t\t  https://guitarmagazine.jp/for_beginners/2021-0824-shibanzukun-seminar-28/",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673534299,
      "updated": 1673534299
    },
    {
      "id": "63c01b5aaff09e0000216312",
      "text": "\t\t  TDSと構成音が被ってるやつを同一視する([代理コード])",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673534299,
      "updated": 1673534299
    },
    {
      "id": "63c01b5aaff09e0000216313",
      "text": "\t\t  \t「TDSと3個中2個構成音が被ってるやつを同一視する」なら3は3=1で3=5になるし、6はわざわざ転回してトニックだと説明してるけど、転回しなくても4=6だし、この説明は支離滅裂に感じました[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673534299,
      "updated": 1673540037
    },
    {
      "id": "63c02612774b170000d51804",
      "text": "\t\t  他の同様の図[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673537043,
      "updated": 1673537108
    },
    {
      "id": "63c0266c774b170000d51808",
      "text": "\t\t   [https://gyazo.com/4f915efa6af1519fea1c7d381a19dcbd]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673537132,
      "updated": 1673537138
    },
    {
      "id": "63c02687774b170000d5180a",
      "text": "\t\t    https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-319-16498-4_16",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673537160,
      "updated": 1673537162
    },
    {
      "id": "63c02f55aff09e000021631f",
      "text": "\t\t   \tこれは納得感ある[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673539413,
      "updated": 1673539413
    },
    {
      "id": "63c02f1eaff09e000021631e",
      "text": "\t\t\t    T: 1,3,6,  D: 3,5,7,   S:2,4,6と書いている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673539359,
      "updated": 1673539432
    },
    {
      "id": "63c02f5eaff09e0000216320",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t    つまり[\" 3は3=1で3=5]だから3はTonic(1)にもDominant(5)にも含まれるってことだよね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673539422,
      "updated": 1673539969
    },
    {
      "id": "63c02f99aff09e0000216321",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t    [\" 6は...転回しなくても4=6]だから6はSubdominant(4)にも含まれている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673539481,
      "updated": 1673539570
    },
    {
      "id": "63c56e80aff09e0000255d3a",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t  [https://gyazo.com/655ec209e8a12da151f197a2b56ed192]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673883265,
      "updated": 1673883274
    },
    {
      "id": "63c56e77aff09e0000255d39",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t  \thttps://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/和声",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673883255,
      "updated": 1673883262
    },
    {
      "id": "63c56e8eaff09e0000255d3c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t  \tこれも同じコンセプト[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673883279,
      "updated": 1673883297
    },
    {
      "id": "63c6a031774b1700002a343c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t  \t何の音がなっているのかわかりやすい[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673961521,
      "updated": 1673961536
    },
    {
      "id": "63c02640774b170000d51806",
      "text": "\t\t   [https://gyazo.com/9abaf1bd7ef4965c8beeb49007cc6ae5]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673537089,
      "updated": 1673537093
    },
    {
      "id": "63c02618774b170000d51805",
      "text": "\t\t    https://www.researchgate.net/figure/2-D-visualisation-of-the-diatonic-triads-of-the-C-major-region-in-the-Tonal-Interval_fig6_303595116",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673537049,
      "updated": 1673537095
    },
    {
      "id": "63c02649774b170000d51807",
      "text": "\t\t   \tこれも納得感ある[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673537097,
      "updated": 1673539583
    },
    {
      "id": "63c02eafaff09e000021631d",
      "text": "\t\t   \t\t7つのコードに本質的な境界などなく円環状の構造であって、人間が適当に境界を引いただけということ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673539247,
      "updated": 1673554585
    },
    {
      "id": "63e531e9774b170000c4f1d0",
      "text": "\t\t   [https://gyazo.com/ae313cc0fc3744dfa31f5485b5d789ca]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1675964906,
      "updated": 1675964908
    },
    {
      "id": "63e531f2774b170000c4f1d2",
      "text": "\t\t    [https://soundquest.jp/quest/nexus-system/control-factors/ 接続系理論 ❶ コントロール・ファクター - SoundQuest]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1675964915,
      "updated": 1675964924
    },
    {
      "id": "63e531ec774b170000c4f1d1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1675964908,
      "updated": 1675964908
    },
    {
      "id": "63c01b5aaff09e000021631c",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/c07c9f8b469c47562ba326cb295b0cef https://youtu.be/Hym5OZVK6X0?t=517]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673534299,
      "updated": 1673880324
    },
    {
      "id": "63c562f1aff09e0000255d26",
      "text": "　　3のEm(3)をC(1)と同様のトニックだとみなしてトニックとして使うこと([代理コード])の問題点が解説されてた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673880305,
      "updated": 1673880647
    },
    {
      "id": "63c56373aff09e00004ae064",
      "text": "　　　やっぱり[\" 3は3=1で3=5]だから3はTonic(1)の性格もDominant(5)の性格も持つという話",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673880435,
      "updated": 1673880574
    },
    {
      "id": "63c563feaff09e00004ae065",
      "text": "　　　そのせいで5→3は分類通りのD→Tのような落ち着きがない、ということが実例を挙げて説明されている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673880574,
      "updated": 1673880623
    },
    {
      "id": "63c562bdaff09e0000255d25",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673880253,
      "updated": 1673880253
    },
    {
      "id": "63c01b44aff09e0000216307",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673534276,
      "updated": 1673534276
    },
    {
      "id": "63c01b44aff09e0000216308",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673534276,
      "updated": 1673534276
    },
    {
      "id": "63c000e1aff09e0000e53059",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673527521,
      "updated": 1673527521
    },
    {
      "id": "63c000e1aff09e0000e5305a",
      "text": "https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/自然の諸原理に還元された和声論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673527521,
      "updated": 1673527528
    },
    {
      "id": "63c000e2aff09e0000e5305b",
      "text": "\t>[ジャン＝フィリップ・ラモー]が完成させた音楽に関する教程である。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673527522,
      "updated": 1673527550
    },
    {
      "id": "63c000f8aff09e0000e5305c",
      "text": "\t>和音に対して「[転回]」という概念を初めて持ち込み、フランス以外のヨーロッパの音楽家によって激しく抗議された",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673527544,
      "updated": 1673527591
    },
    {
      "id": "63c00124aff09e0000e5305d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673527589,
      "updated": 1673527589
    },
    {
      "id": "63c0a9a76eb4060000088df8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1673570727,
      "updated": 1673570727
    },
    {
      "id": "63c0a9976eb4060000088df6",
      "text": "数字で書いてあるところがパッと理解できないので後でじっくり読みたい[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
